      "beast_baseline": "i mean i get what you're saying about the science, but like, is it really that big of a deal? i only have like half a glass most days and i've been doing it for months without any issues. it seems like a bit much to say i'm basically overdosing just because of a little bit of juice. can't i just take my pill a few hours apart from breakfast to be safe? surely that would stop the interaction from happening?",
